cdata.name: Zero
cdata.desc: Zerois fork of Zcash (Zcash is fork of Bitcoin). It has the security of Bitcoin, the privacy of Zcash and few other improvements. Zeroincludes the best privacy and anonymity technology available today. The coin hasno founders reward, no premine, no slow start and no block reward halving. The developers have alsoabandoned idea of mining on mobile devices and made the mining parameters harder.
